Recreate this classic set with Spectras!: https://www.emazinglights.com/products/spectra-bluetooth-glove-set

A true piece of light show history. The first video on our channel to reach over 1 million views from one of gloving's most influential figures of all time. This set was built to remind of the stars and cosmos but now it's something so much more. Thanks to everybody who has supported us throughout the years. Oh and we left the original text below if you'd like to see to preserve a bit of the history.

Original set consist of:
6 x PurYB 3c Strobes
2 x ROB 3c Strobes 
Thumbs - ROW Hyper strobe
Plams - Red Solid

Original Text:
DJ Gummy's brand new set - Nebula! This set reminded us the stars and cosmos, hence the name nebula. We think its a great combination of colors...but don't take our word for it. Watch the featured video above to check it out in action!
